## 🔒 Security Implemented

| Feature | Details |
|---------|---------|
| SHA-256 password | Web Crypto API, never stored plain |
| Rate limiting | 5 attempts → 30s lockout, in-memory |
| Session | Memory-only, 2h timeout, never in localStorage |
| XSS | React JSX auto-escaping + manual esc() on templates |
| URL validation | Only http/https accepted for images |
| Phone validation | Israeli + international formats |
| Amount validation | Server: min ₪10, max ₪100,000 |
| Admin token | Constant-time comparison in Hono Worker |
| CORS | Locked to ALLOWED_ORIGIN env var |
| Server sanitisation | All string fields stripped of `<>"'\`` |
| Duplicate orders | KV checks for existing order ID before insert |
| CSP headers | `_headers` file: Stripe, fonts, no inline eval |

